        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the site 
        constitutes acceptance of any changes.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
